Formula is a library for generating HTML5 forms and validating data.

It subscribes to the MicroPHP Manifesto approach to doing things...


Notes (organize):
API:
* Add Elements
* Add elements hierarchially via fieldsets
* Build
* Validate

It should:
* Build a form
* Export JSON representation of the form (for JS rendering)
* Validate form data or arbitrary data
* The form API can be used only for validation (not rendering)

Elements:
* Name
* Type
* Options
* Default
* Required
* Validation
* Style Classes
* Custom Attributes
* Description
* Placeholder
* After
* Before
* ..
